Uses twitter4r (http://twitter4r.rubyforge.org/) by Susan Potter for twitter backend.
Uses metafusion-crypto (http://snakesgemscoffee.blogspot.com/2007/10/democratic-debate-ann-coulter-and.html) by Susan Potter for crypto library.

